  "detailed_description": "Pester was released on Xbox live indies back in early 2013 and was Flump Studios first game developed for public release.<br>A remake of one of my early C64 games, Pester is a very fast paced and busy vertical shooter.<br>Graphically remastered with new sprite work from Dylan Barry and a thumping soundtrack from Matt Macfarland.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Intense old school action</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tate support</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Customisable play options, over 100 combinations of play</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Remastered sprite work from Dylan Barry</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Thumping soundtrack from Matt Macfarland</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Pester was released on Xbox live indies back in early 2013 and was Flump Studios first game developed for public release.<br>A remake of one of my early C64 games, Pester is a very fast paced and busy vertical shooter.<br>Graphically remastered with new sprite work from Dylan Barry and a thumping soundtrack from Matt Macfarland.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Intense old school action</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tate support</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Customisable play options, over 100 combinations of play</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Remastered sprite work from Dylan Barry</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Thumping soundtrack from Matt Macfarland</li></ul>",
